{"title":"牡丹花开放了——西藏新民歌选","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1959,"month":4,"day":22}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"牡丹花开放了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——西藏新民歌选"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳和月亮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席像太阳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席像月亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳出来万物能生长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月亮出来黑夜行人有方向。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席的恩情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席的恩情，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像冬天的阳光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们沐浴在里面，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"充满了幸福和希望。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来了亲人解放军"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来了亲人解放军，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"发放了无利贷款，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苦难深重的人们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走向吉祥如意的世界。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的亲人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"关心我们的是领袖毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无利贷款的是人民解放军，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"压迫我们的是帝国主义，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"帮助我们的是救星毛主席。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们心里明白："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁是我们的亲人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁是我们的仇敌！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牡丹花开放了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国的西方有块最好的地方，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在那里长的有最美的牡丹花；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但是在过去牡丹花从未开放，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——因为水深火热。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"现在牡丹花开放了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席引着我们从花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丛中走出来。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不雕的花朵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同一父母生下来的孩子呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"本来就是亲兄弟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生活在毛主席的太阳下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"愿我们万寿无疆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山头上开了千年不败"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"的牡丹花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人们生活在鲜花里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"愿它永远不雕谢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跟着解放军"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白天见了解放军，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如同见太阳！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑夜见了解放军，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如同见月亮！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远跟着您呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大道儿明光光！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}